Enterprise

Ben Porterfield is one half of the founding team at Looker, a smarter business intelligence tool. Connected through our Partner Bill Trenchard, we saw Porterfield’s surfer-engineer ethos and Lloyd Tabb’s seasoned technical leadership as a perfect blend. They’ve went on to serve up insights to hundreds of major customers and were acquired by Google for $2.6 billion in 2019.
